message: 1、修复部分系统报odm分区不可读写的bug||2、适配更多系统的，之前模拟成功，刷卡失败的可以试试（需要先清除APP缓存）||3、修复已知bug
message_en: 1. Fix the bug that some systems report that the odm partition is not readable and writable.||2. Adapt to more systems (need to clear the APP cache first).||3. General stability & performance improvements.
